data.description: This is a gorgeous remodeled home in Central Gardens with a large front porch and swing. There is a large den in front which opens into the dining room, and there are 2 spacious Bedrooms. There is a large master bath w/ a walk in shower and one of the things missing from so many midtown homes, a massive walk in closet. The remodeled kitchen has updated appliances and cabinets and plenty of counter space. H/W Floors are all flat and in good shape w/ extra storage in the building out back.
